Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.33,0:00:06.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, y'all! C'mon up to the seashell shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.93,0:00:08.40,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"20 Yen"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:08.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Should be around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:17.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please search carefully today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:20.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to stay at the camping site anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:21.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:25.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's the seashell shop. C'mon up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:30.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:33.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:35.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! C'mon up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the competitiveness?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:41.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you playing shop? What are you selling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:42.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seashells.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:45.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, can I get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:48.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you liked kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:51.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Officially, anyway.\N--You're pretty terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:53.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Kawafuji-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:57.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Give this one another ten years, and I could like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not liking kids. That's liking women.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Specifically, I like my women--ahem--{\i1}mature.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:05.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Eew! Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.49,0:01:09.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--The heck?! You trying to break my glasses?!\N--Eew, yuck! Something got on me! So disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:13.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You use a toothpick to dig 'em out like this, and eat 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:16.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Eew! Gross, gross, gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:15.60,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"*Good kids don't eat them raw!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:17.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Little girl...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:20.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a person named\NHanda Seishu living around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:24.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa... Seishu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:25.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:26.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:30.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a sensei with a fancy name like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:31.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A calligraphy sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:37.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's him! Do you know where Handa-{\i1}sensei{\i0} lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:39.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you if you buy a seashell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty shrewd.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:42.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, then sell me that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:46.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Quite an eye to choose this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:51.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But only a rich person like an IT prez or a major leaguer can buy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:56.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...how's about a card payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:57.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C-Card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:01:59.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, how much do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.98,0:02:02.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be my guide too, so I'll pay you good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mi... Mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A million yen to you, ya thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like a thief when\NI haven't bargained a single yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:14.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I never saw one before... So this is a card...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:16.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:19.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right, little girl. Take us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:22.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec! I'm gonna show this to grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now just you wait! My stuff is first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:26.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:27.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and take us--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd ya come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:32.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Head Teach?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:36.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--We got some weird folks here.\N--Kidnappers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:37.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look at them tattoos he's got.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah, well, it's not what you...\N--Call the fire squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:41.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go to the village meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear what ya have ta say there, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:45.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:48.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji-{\i1}san{\i0}--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.99,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Yosonmon"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.99,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,76)}"Translation: The guys from Tokyo"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:33.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why are you two eating at my place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:37.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dad and Mom went to the village meeting at the community center.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:41.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes better than eating alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:43.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind eating alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:48.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you got fat since you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:55.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The country's loose atmosphere is spoiling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Men with a little meat are just right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:04.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it's been bothering me for a bit, but what's with the scribbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I met a guy who had scribbles on him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not a "normal" guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:12.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Scribbles? More like tattoos, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:16.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A flower... Dog... What are those dots?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:16.34,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Dog"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Marble chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:21.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did that guy's tattoo look like an eagle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It was all messy and I couldn't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:28.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually gotten a ton of emails from him since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:36.03,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Kawafuji"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:36.03,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,76)}"Kawafuji"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:36.03,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,107)}"Kawafuji"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:36.03,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,138)}"Kawafuji"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That may be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:36.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After falling in the sea a number of times, the keys were acting up and I couldn't reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:40.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the mobile,\NI'm surprised that you have a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:43.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm gonna beat you.\N--Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha mean, "What's the matter?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:53.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys, come in from here!\NThat's the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:57.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'd prefer you use the entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:02.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're saying they're your friends, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:05.09,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Drunk"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeaaah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kawa... fuji...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:10.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he so out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Something like, he was gonna kidnap some kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:15.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,so he was being lectured until now at the village meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're exactly righty...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:19.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But with all the people, it just became a drinking get-together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:21.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm sooo sorry...\N--Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Heeey, Handa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:29.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You... Do you even know how worried I was for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:33.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A city boy like you living in the country like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Great, so now you're going to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was just so worried, and worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You were this worried for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My friend Handa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My friend Kawafuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:47.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My friend forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Crane-style!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:57.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you freakin' ignore my calls?!\NAre you fake?! Are you a fake friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:59.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! My mobile was acting up, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:02.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you! Do whatcha need to do to call me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I figured you would find your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Don't underestimate the inconvenience of the rural!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:14.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?! The hell are you doing barfing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been a pain coming from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:21.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It took about three hours by plane with connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:25.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. I'm still not sure how to ride a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:27.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even been on one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You kids never went to Tokyo before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Nope.\N--Only as far as Nagasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For me, Hyogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:37.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sensei? We're outta {\i1}konomon{\i0}["pickles"].\NCan ya get more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:40.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Get more? Are you asking an elder to do stuff for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is your house, Sensei, so c'mon, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--You're all like friends.\N--Middle schoolers nowadays...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem like Sensei's friend, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...did you just come along with the drunk over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to meet Handa-{\i1}san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.91,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Kanzaki Kosuke"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a calligrapher, Kanzaki Kosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:08:01.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Naru wanna card too. Naru too.\N--I was drawn to calligraphy through my admiration of Handa-{\i1}san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Naru too. Naru too!\N--Huh... But you look super young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Naru too!! Naru too!\N--I'm eighteen. I get mistaken for a middle schooler a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Yay!\N--An eighteen-year-old calligrapher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd I hear this before...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:17.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, I mustered the courage to challenge the Tokyo Kasho Exhibit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:19.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The same exhibit that Handa-{\i1}san{\i0} submitted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:20.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm so bad with sensing the mood of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:27.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I actually took first place from the person I admire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:32.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly felt closer to Handa-{\i1}san,{\i0} who I thought was unreachable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:36.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess Handa-{\i1}san{\i0} wasn't serious back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:39.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this the guy he was talkin' about?\NY'know, the mochi toss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:42.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the "second place" incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The heck is he planning to do, coming to see Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he came just to see him bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:51.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If Sensei finds out who he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is this much {\i1}konomon{\i0} enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:54.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Handa-{\i1}san{\i0}, here's my card...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Nooo!\N--Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "no"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you normally eat this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:00.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't about the amount!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's too much! How hooked are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:07.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the funny type, aren't you, Handa-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:10.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man, if he finds out he lost to this tacky guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And with how much pride Sensei has...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...he could commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-{\i1}san{\i0}, about the last exhibit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:23.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You gotta go soon!\NYou're staying at an inn, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We stayed overnight at a campsite yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? Then ya gotta go back to Camp Village, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Walking the road at night's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji is sleeping, so why don't you stay here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:39.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. I didn't like the campsite with all the bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, there's a lot I wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:44.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So what now? He's all into staying over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we better stay over too and stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:48.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a career advising\NI gotta be at tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:49.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:55.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's friend is Naru's friend, so here's a sign of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A dirty Monster Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--What the heck did ya do?!\N--Naru's precious buggies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:09.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't keep weird pets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Be quiet...\N--Damn it! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:14.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, Sensei! Don't agitate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?! Stink?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See?! I told ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}!\N--'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:22.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you use this, you can catch 'em without 'em stinkin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:32.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You guys know the strangest stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:35.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's super useful, so don't call it "strange."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No more... I wanna go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You should just go back for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:43.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The smell is gonna attract more of them bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:47.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:48.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:52.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Handa-{\i1}san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:57.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can I... call you "Sensei" too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We made it through...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:09.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, so that's Kanzaki Kosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:13.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't look the type to be doing calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The dirty side of him was coming out, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:19.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait a sec! You knew him?!\N--Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.68,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"From: Kawafuji
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.68,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}Sub: Answer the phone!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:22.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not personally, but I did get an email from Kawafuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:28.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll bring along the brat, Kanzaki Kosuke, who won first place at the exhibit."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"He's a bit unique, so be prepared."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--See?\N--Not "see"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't ya tell how stressed we were back there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:44.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that it doesn't bother me, and I am envious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...I feel more at ease than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go and catch the remaining bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to bother you again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:01.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is tea okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji isn't coming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.65,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Sun Sun Camp Village"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:08.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He has a major hangover, and can't even get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he can be like that at times...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:15.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Like, he always does things at the wrong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:19.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Tea in this heat...?\N--Tea has got to be black bean tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear anything about me from Kawafuji-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:25.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Something about you getting first place, and it went to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:31.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of respect for you, Handa-{\i1}sensei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:34.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:37.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I collected all the publications\NI could that you appeared in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:45.46,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"All You Need to Know About Calligraphy"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:45.46,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,76)}"Learning from Scratch:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:45.46,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,107)}Introduction to Calligraphy"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The talented calligrapher with a master calligrapher as a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:45.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All the publications give praise that Sensei's words are true to fundamentals, and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:47.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See the smug look on the gravure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:50.36,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Calligrapher
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:50.36,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,73)}Handa Seishu"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make an expression like this without confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In this one, you're in a black suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Was it black to represent ink?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.87,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Handa Seishu"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:59.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? This is just embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:03.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see? Sensei, you're the one who I want to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:06.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of, I love this comment the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:12.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"...breathe in the refined air, and when\NI speak to the paper and brush...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:15.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--...they listen, and answer back to me.\N--Stop it! Don't read it out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:21.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,To me, calligraphy is a cathartic activity."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:23.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's karuta-sushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.46,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Karuta" "Sushi"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:26.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't console me in silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:29.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is even more wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:31.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the disgrace! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who's meaner here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You did come to mock me, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to hear Sensei's neat lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I even brought a voice recorder for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:44.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a fan are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:48.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I entered the Kasho Exhibit was to meet you, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:51.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in the country like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, the calligraphy that was entered in the exhibit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:57.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...was what you wrote after you came to this island, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:14:00.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Let's go back to Tokyo together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:09.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:14.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We came to see Kanzaki-{\i1}kun{\i0}, but where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:17.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he's at Handa's place now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:18.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:24.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? You came to warn him not to shoot his mouth off to Handa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:26.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't easy keeping watch over an adult, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we're takin' care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:36.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say any more.\NI know exactly how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:43.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how he looks, he's quite a handful, so someone's gotta support him from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:47.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Handa are friends from back in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:50.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--He always had the hardest time being social...\N--Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:53.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...and each time he opened his mouth, he only spoke high-handedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--He gets depressed easily,\N--I'm such a loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--and closes himself off from others.\N--A barrier...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:01.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, he even raised his fist against the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:03.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You can't imagine the pain of cleaning up after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:06.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can actually imagine that easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:10.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought being in the country required being social with others...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:14.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...so I thought he was going to give up right away and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:18.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He must really be enjoying his life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:21.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep an eye out for him a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:26.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you know so much about Sensei, why'd ya bring Kanzaki-{\i1}kun{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:30.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei was super depressed when he lost first place to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Another headache...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an art dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:40.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa's my golden goose before he's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:41.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Golden goose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:45.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I need to have him write quality works or I'd be in trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:48.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's gotten close to finding something since he came to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:52.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He probably just doesn't know what, which is why he's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:56.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A person needs a rival to become better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:01.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I still got a hangover, so I'm gonna sleep it off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:04.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let Handa know I'll stop by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:08.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That sure is Sensei's friend, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:12.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is this like a "sparing the club and spoiling the child" thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:15.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, is calligraphy about winning and losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:16.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not like it's martial arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:21.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please return to Tokyo and face calligraphy seriously like before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:26.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I came to this island to raise my skills in calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back until I see results.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Results?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:32.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "results," Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:38.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'd been doing calligraphy since elementary school, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:43.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...every day was just more boring practice, and I was thinking of quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:48.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that I reluctantly went along to an exhibit and saw your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:53.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And what a beautiful work it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:59.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But now, before even getting results, you've lost your touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Lost my touch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:02.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, your calligraphy is trying to be too unique, or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:08.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...just being written by inspiration, and it isn't like you, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Losing to me is proof of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:16.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be bitter, but you aren't noticing that you've gotten worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This environment is ruining you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:21.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:26.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said that writing to be recognized by others is everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:29.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What an uninteresting piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:32.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So young, yet already writing in monotony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:34.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Very textbook-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:37.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Did you try to overcome the wall of mediocrity?\N--Sensei! Listen to what I have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:40.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I just wanna have fun writing without worrying 'bout that.\N--Let's go back, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Recognized by...?\N--Staying here isn't good for you, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Sen--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aah! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:51.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After winning first, but being told that my calligraphy is uninteresting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:54.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...I then write something good, but don't get first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:57.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so confused...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:01.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no clue what's right anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:08.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A paper airplane?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:09.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's from my collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:19.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Naru, your airplanes fly so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They fly when the wind blows!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:25.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Look at 'em fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:30.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:33.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck! Sensei, say something to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:39.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The beautiful words you saw
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:43.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,are well-behaved words written exactly how my father told me to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:47.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine being reprimanded, as long as...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:51.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...I write words that only I,\NHanda Seishu, can write.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:58.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...I feel it isn't right for me to rush back to Tokyo because of what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You girls, it's dangerous up there. Come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay!\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:15.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You go on ahead and wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:18.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ride the wind, and get to you quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:21.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Can you say that line one more time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:26.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, shoot! That worked better than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! Bring the Village Leader over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hina! Go and get some ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:40.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's still going to get better...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do better too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:49.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:55.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It feels better making dinner with young folks around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,An old hag like you shouldn't be actin' like some tween...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:20:00.19,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"(Dialect) I'm going to beat you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:20:00.19,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}until your jaws come off"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:20:01.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna wallop ya an' crack them jaw bones of yers until ya lose 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:07.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru was passing out mags like this to everyone in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:10.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you're really famous, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:12.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah, um, eh...\N--Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can you autograph this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Does your mom have a grudge against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:23.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, man. In the first place, asking for an autograph...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:29.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you said earlier that everyone in the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:31.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aah... Go figure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:36.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--That's really somethin', bein' published in Tokyo!\N--Can I get your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have an autograph sheet, so can you write on my shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ya ain't a sensei fer nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:44.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,To me, calligraphy is to breathe in the refined air...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:47.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Aah...! Stop!\N--...a cathartic activity...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:50.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home to Tokyo--!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:23.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A dirty Monster Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.77,0:22:25.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:26.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't keep weird pets!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:28.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--They went there!\N--Be quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:31.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, help me! I wanna go back to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:33.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:34.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.21,0:22:37.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous... Dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:39.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, can I let it go...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:44.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The combatants...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They've multiplied...!
